  <entry>
    <title>中国的抑郁症概况</title>
    <link href="/chinese-depression/"/>
    <url>/chinese-depression/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<ul><li><strong>总体患病率</strong>：中国成人的抑郁症终生患病率约为6.8%，其中抑郁症为3.4%，心境恶劣障碍为1.4%，未特定型抑郁障碍为3.2%。过去12个月的抑郁症患病率为3.6%，其中抑郁症为2.1%。</li><li><strong>青少年情况</strong>：在青少年群体中，抑郁症的检出率较高。2020年的数据显示，约24.6%的青少年存在抑郁症状，其中重度抑郁的比例为7.4%。</li><li><strong>治疗现状</strong>：尽管抑郁症的患病率较高，但接受规范治疗的比例较低。数据显示，中国约有91.9%的抑郁症患者没有接受过专业的精神科治疗，仅有约8.1%的患者获得了治疗。<br>这些数据表明，中国的抑郁症患者人数众多，但治疗覆盖率较低，需要进一步提升公众对抑郁症的认识以及改善心理健康服务的可及性。<br>（来源：ChatGPT）<br>文章来源：<br><a href="https://www.163.com/jiankang/article/GKRGNPJG0038950F.html#:~:text=%E6%A0%B9%E6%8D%AE%E2%80%9C%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85%E8%B4%9F%E6%8B%85%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E2%80%9D%202019%E5%B9%B4%E5%85%AC%E5%B8%83%E7%9A%84%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E6%8A%A5%E5%91%8A%EF%BC%8C%E6%97%A0%E8%AE%BA%E5%9C%A8%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E8%BF%98%E6%98%AF%E5%9C%A8%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%EF%BC%8C%E6%8A%91%E9%83%81%E9%9A%9C%E7%A2%8D%E5%9C%A8%E7%B2%BE%E7%A5%9E%E9%9A%9C%E7%A2%8D%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85%E8%B4%9F%E6%8B%85%E5%9D%87%E5%B1%85%E9%A6%96%E4%BD%8D%EF%BC%9B%E5%9C%A8%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E6%89%80%E6%9C%89%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85%E7%9A%84%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85%E8%B4%9F%E6%8B%85%E4%B8%AD%E6%8A%91%E9%83%81%E9%9A%9C%E7%A2%8D%E6%8E%92%E5%90%8D%E7%AC%AC13%E4%BD%8D%EF%BC%8C%E5%9C%A8%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E6%8E%92%E5%90%8D%E7%AC%AC11%E4%BD%8D%E3%80%82%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E7%9A%84%E6%8A%91%E9%83%81%E9%9A%9C%E7%A2%8D%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85%E8%B4%9F%E6%8B%85%E9%AB%98%EF%BC%8C%E7%84%B6%E8%80%8C%E4%B9%8B%E5%89%8D%E5%B9%B6%E6%B2%A1%E6%9C%89%E5%85%B7%E6%9C%89%E5%85%A8%E5%9B%BD%E4%BB%A3%E8%A1%A8%E6%80%A7%E7%9A%84%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E3%80%82%E4%B8%BA%E6%AD%A4%EF%BC%8C%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E7%BB%84%E6%B7%B1%E5%85%A5%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90%E4%BA%86%E2%80%9C%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E7%B2%BE%E7%A5%9E%E5%8D%AB%E7%94%9F%E8%B0%83%E6%9F%A5%E2%80%9D%E4%B8%AD%E5%85%B3%E4%BA%8E%E6%8A%91%E9%83%81%E9%9A%9C%E7%A2%8D%E7%9A%84%E6%82%A3%E7%97%85%E7%8E%87%E5%8F%8A%E5%8D%AB%E7%94%9F%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E5%88%A9%E7%94%A8%E6%83%85%E5%86%B5%EF%BC%8C%E6%8F%8F%E8%BF%B0%E4%BA%86%E6%8A%91%E9%83%81%E9%9A%9C%E7%A2%8D%E7%9A%84%E